Welcome back, @mcdsg ❤

Most #mcdsg restaurants will open starting today, 11 May from 7am to 9pm. Those located in parks, tourists attractions, institutions as well as dessert kiosks & @mccafesg will remain closed.

If you're planning to do takeaway, rmb to observe all safety measures. Or simply order via McDelivery or @grabfoodsg.

P.s. this photo was taken back in July 2019

Photo by Calvin Lee | Singapore Foodie on May 10, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'We're back. No rush. Stay safe. #SGunited M While our restaurants have reopened from May 11, the McDonald's App is not in operation for the time being. Please check back again for deals after the Circuit Breaker period ending June In the the meantime, you can still enjoy your McDonald's favourites via contactless McDelivery®, Drive-Thru and takeaway.'

Photo by Calvin Lee | Singapore Foodie on May 10, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'Thank you for choosing McDelivery! Our current operating hours is to 9:00pm (last order at 8:30pm). All in the spirit of safety first, we've gone 100% contactless delivery and will only be accepting cashless payments. To give our customers a pleasant ordering experience, are using virtual queue system to limit the number of customers accessing the McDelivery portal at the same time. Please do not close or this page as you are being placed in the queue. Thank you for your patience! Sincerely, Your McDelivery® team'
